--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    m3uer
    current version:        0.1.0
    by:                     Rikard Johansson
    license:                GPL 3.0
    dependencies:           Ext JS (http://dev.sencha.com)

    Simple remote m3u playlist generator and editor. It is developed to be used
    on a remote server containing all media files and playlists.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.1.0, 2011-02-16
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * File config.php for easy setup
    * Tree view of playlists
    * Tree view of media files in given playlist
    * List of playlist contents
    * Add new playlist
    * Delete existing playlists
    * Edit existing playlists
    * Cascade checking of songs in playlist recursive (both up and down)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
